    * [OHAI-6] - CLI output should allow filtering based on attribute
    * [OHAI-67] - language/perl plugin
    * [OHAI-75] - Need perl language bindings
    * [OHAI-80] - Enable incremental updates of ohai data
    * [OHAI-85] - Add DMI information

